            "aws-cn": "Gateway Load Balancer uses Gateway Load Balancer Endpoint (GWLBE), a new type of VPC Endpoint powered by Amazon PrivateLink technology that simplifies how applications can securely exchange traffic with GWLB across VPC boundaries. GWLBE is priced and billed separately."
